  "remarks": "Aleksandr Sychugov is the General Director of JSC “Voskresensky Aggregation Factory” and was previously the General Director of Federal State Enterprise “Voskresensk State Aggregate Plant” from 24 September 2018 until the reorganisation of the company on 31 January 2023. Therefore, Sychugov has been the General Director and thus the main decision-maker of “Voskresensky Aggregation Factory” since 24 September 2018.",
